  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/1b6570befc43348c0aecfc97fd44ee87.poster.avif?t=1724161110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/1b6570befc43348c0aecfc97fd44ee87.webm?t=1724161110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/1b6570befc43348c0aecfc97fd44ee87.mp4?t=1724161110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The unique spot the difference game <strong>Poltergeist Watcher</strong> blends elements of hidden object, mindfulness puzzles, and psychological horror genres. It will evoke tension and fear in the most unconventional settings for these genres. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/99e00c009a3b007b2355926e1559b7fc.poster.avif?t=1724161110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/99e00c009a3b007b2355926e1559b7fc.webm?t=1724161110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/99e00c009a3b007b2355926e1559b7fc.mp4?t=1724161110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Inspired by cult paranormal films, this game will immerse you in the ominous atmosphere of an ancient mansion consumed by poltergeist activity. To survive, you'll need keen observation, a good memory, and unwavering willpower, because ghost will do everything to scare who are watching him.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/1b6570befc43348c0aecfc97fd44ee87.poster.avif?t=1724161110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/1b6570befc43348c0aecfc97fd44ee87.webm?t=1724161110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/1b6570befc43348c0aecfc97fd44ee87.mp4?t=1724161110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The unique spot the difference game <strong>Poltergeist Watcher</strong> blends elements of hidden object, mindfulness puzzles, and psychological horror genres. It will evoke tension and fear in the most unconventional settings for these genres. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/99e00c009a3b007b2355926e1559b7fc.poster.avif?t=1724161110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/99e00c009a3b007b2355926e1559b7fc.webm?t=1724161110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2926550/extras/99e00c009a3b007b2355926e1559b7fc.mp4?t=1724161110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Inspired by cult paranormal films, this game will immerse you in the ominous atmosphere of an ancient mansion consumed by poltergeist activity. To survive, you'll need keen observation, a good memory, and unwavering willpower, because ghost will do everything to scare who are watching him.",
